{
  "texts": [
    "For example, Meta's Oversight Board has geographic diversity requirements in its bylaws [129].",
    "They should adequately represent historically marginalized communities [26,103].Board members may be more or less senior.",
    "By \"seniority\", we mean a person's position of status which typically corresponds to their work experience and is reflected in their title.",
    "More senior people tend to have more subject-matter expertise.",
    "And the board of directors and senior management might take them more seriously."
  ]
}